cdata.name: Dataeum
cdata.desc:
Dataeum is a Blockchain-based collaborative platform for physical data generation. Its primary objective is to create an ecosystem where users can gather physical data (from stores, gas stations, traffic signs, etc) and then make it available in a decentralized marketplace, trough the platform's app. Datareum expects to be successful in gathering 100% of the physical data in the world.

The XDT token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency developed by the Dataeum. It is the token that will serve as a medium of exchange value within the platform and can be related to Data collection, Data licensing, Merchants interaction, as well as other Dataeum supported services.
